    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家交流群：811595629</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《牢笼都市》是一款末日丧尸题材俯视角射击游戏，融合了探索、生存和战斗元素。你将扮演一名失忆的士兵，穿梭在丧尸横行的城市废墟中，探索未知的区域，收集资源，寻找线索，并与各类怪物进行生死较量。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开放世界探索</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要在一个庞大的开放世界城市中进行探索，收集物资，维持生存，同时抵御散布在城市中的各类丧尸与怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/678dee495129e0b75f4c363f146e07e9.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/678dee495129e0b75f4c363f146e07e9.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/678dee495129e0b75f4c363f146e07e9.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的枪械</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中既提供了手枪、自动步枪、霰弹枪、榴弹发射器等传统武器，也提供了喷火器、电磁枪等科幻武器，为你提供丰富的射击体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/3aababb6189886ff722d426558c16a0e.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/3aababb6189886ff722d426558c16a0e.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/3aababb6189886ff722d426558c16a0e.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多样的技能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以通过拾取到的神秘物品解锁技能树中的技能，也可以将货币供奉给石像以提升属性值，并且在击败强敌后，还能获得强力的永久被动技能效果。随着探索的深入，你的战斗体验将越来越丰富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/cb31ac887cfa120077f9a95d66ed4bee.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/cb31ac887cfa120077f9a95d66ed4bee.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/cb31ac887cfa120077f9a95d66ed4bee.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >交易系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以将拾取到杂物交换为货币，亦可以在售货机处购买需要的物资。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/1d7408bce64055d4686f3cc03b7cba4f.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/1d7408bce64055d4686f3cc03b7cba4f.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/1d7408bce64055d4686f3cc03b7cba4f.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地牢探险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入探索危机四伏的地牢，击败成群的怪物，以带回重要的物资。地牢中有极其危险的生物，它们似乎在守护什么？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/70ab7dd3037a5f687990801e3b95620d.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/70ab7dd3037a5f687990801e3b95620d.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/70ab7dd3037a5f687990801e3b95620d.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引人入胜的剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着探索的深入，你将逐步揭开灾难背后的真相，同时直面那不可名状之物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/30f4796bf5d3667dec0382aebb5f507a.poster.avif?t=1768834202\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/30f4796bf5d3667dec0382aebb5f507a.webm?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3140050/extras/30f4796bf5d3667dec0382aebb5f507a.mp4?t=1768834202\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
